    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, this is certainly a pickleball match. There are people hitting a ball over a net. Some of them are quite good at it, others... less so. It's a real nail-biter, or perhaps a paddle-pusher, if you will. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
